{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Read-only metadata utilities for REAPER items:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Unwrap SECTION to real parent source\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Read iXML TRACK_LIST (Wave Agent style)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Fallback parse sTRK#=Name from BWF/Description (EdiLoad split)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Interleave index \u8596 ? recorder channel mapping\par}
