{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 AudioSweet Solo Toggle\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Toggles solo state for the AudioSweet target track.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Behavior\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Track Solo Mode (preview_solo_scope = 0)}: \u8226 ? Priority 1: If AudioSweet Preview is active (placeholder found) \u8594 ? Toggle the preview target track \u8226 ? Priority 2: If any track is currently soloed \u8594 ? Toggle that track's solo \u8226 ? Priority 3: No preview/solo \u8594 ? Toggle preview target track solo (from GUI settings)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Item Solo Mode (preview_solo_scope = 1)}: \u8226 ? Toggle solo for selected items (REAPER command 41561)\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Note: Detects active preview via placeholder item, stays locked to preview target track\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Debug Mode\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Set DEBUG = true in script to enable detailed console logging:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab ExtState settings loaded\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Soloed track detection\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Target track resolution steps\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Final solo toggle action\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Requirements\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab AudioSweet ReaImGui GUI for ExtState configuration\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Works independently - can be assigned to keyboard shortcuts in action list\sa180\par}
}

